{"tid":891900,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗拿甸奴喜愛夜蒲，來華踢表演賽一晚召三女郎","createTime":"2018-11-06T13:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T16:08:04.000Z","uid":30040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e5969bb9f0adb6e3500f7ebce4d9f71e414dd3","tid":891900,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"被爆出拖欠200萬歐元罰款及銀行賬戶只餘下6歐元的前巴西國腳朗拿甸奴向來喜愛夜蒲，去年到中國參加表演賽期間更被指一晚召來三名女郎共度春宵。<br />\n<br />\n「細哨」去年率領南美明星隊到中國銀川，與費高率領的歐洲明星隊進行表演賽，結果南美明星隊以1:4敗北，「細哨」則被傳在當地聲色犬馬及耍大牌而成為焦點。<br />\n<br />\n朗拿甸奴去年訪問中國踢表演賽期間，有指他一晚召三名女郎度春宵，網上更流傳疑似「細哨」在夜店包廂消遣的影片，當時其身旁有數名性感女郎。當時亦有網友爆料指他剛剛抵達銀川，便問翻譯哪裏可找到姑娘陪睡，甚至有朗拿甸奴與女郎的自拍照在網上瘋傳，其中一張疑似在酒店房間內拍攝的照片中，「細哨」上身赤裸，女方則身穿制服，有人估計兩人可能在玩角色扮演。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181106/large/1541489579_9bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F1541489579_9bff.jpg&h=06e65365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181106/large/1541489579_9bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181106%2Flarge%2F1541489579_9bff.jpg&h=06e65365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"857d12e893f151cc033c716c316ffa355bec263e","tid":891900,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"森巴屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27859607c8069fb0b6f440102c6d9558a3a8740f","tid":891900,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"朗甸屌女癲"},{"pid":"023234b6117ff000314d9d07caf3ec68d4049ab7","tid":891900,"uid":36724,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"係咁出牛尾巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4699d5c1ced822c4d4a15411e6734f7eae2df654","tid":891900,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor